item.title: How do i get into server with other pepol on it?
item.dc:creator: @TheSorrow TheSorrow
item.description:
@TheSorrow wrote:

Assuming you have moparscape 3.0…

you look on the server advertisement part of this forum…

http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/board,50.0.html

then you copy the ip address or no-ip address you found into the New Server part of moparscape (under File, at the top). Then press OK. Then click on Enter and log on. Sometimes servers are down so you might have to go through a few.

Hope it helps

PS. Pepol isnt a word. It is spelt people
